==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Robbin
<hw>Rob"bin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>A
kind of package in which pepper and other dry commodities are sometimes
exported from the East Indies. The <xex>robbin</xex> of rice in Malabar
weighs about 84 pounds.</def> <rj><au>Simmonds.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Robbin</ent>⟦br⟧

